# ovh_vps_available_image (Data Source)

Use this data source to retrieve information about a specific available image for an OVHcloud VPS.

## Example Usage

{{tffile "examples/data-sources/vps_available_image/example_1.tf"}}

## Argument Reference

* `service_name` - (Required) The service_name of your VPS.
* `id` - (Required) The ID of the image to retrieve.

## Attributes Reference

(See generated docs/data-sources/vps_available_image.md for the full attribute list.)

* `id` - The ID of the image.
* `description` - Description of the image.
* `name` - Name of the image.
* `variant` - Variant of the image.
